PluginData.Author: dogboy
PluginData.Tooltip: Customizable ships sounds, makes your ship alive! Multiplayer compatable!
PluginData.Description:
Adds authentic engine sounds that dynamically respond to your ships speed, maneuvering, startup, hull ambiences and more, providing an immersive GaMInG experience. Choose from a diverse selection of engine addons and switch between them on the move. To add more engines, simply enable them as a client mod OR add them as a mod from workshop for everyone to use. Access menu by presing Ctrl + F1. *Works on the servers aswell.
Allows to make your own sound packs
